<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to WavePay</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #36d299;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #36d299;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to WavePay!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Congratulations! You have successfully onboarded to WavePay.</p>
        <p>We are excited to have you on board. With WavePay, you can easily manage your crypto assets and offramp to
            your local bank account.</p>
        <p>Here are some things you can do:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Complete your KYC verification</li>
            <li>Add your bank account</li>
            <li>Start transacting securely</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The WavePay Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>